name: m_op: 0005
description:
Big Bear, California, USA, Sunday 24th,January 2021, 6:42:35PM
Where the wind blows, where the sea takes me, to lose my soul and on the process a small piece of breath, where the strange becomes familiar, where the familiar becomes unknown. 

I go by mr_oipunx, a stupid mind on a stupid world, looking to create something that has never been created that results familiar to everyone, looking to become no one, while I merge myself with the photos I take, as I leave a little piece of me behind, on every photo and every step; until one there there is no more to share.
